      "text": "Could someone send 1 liter of SESO to:\n\nVictor Heininger\n139 Gulbrandsen Road, \nOrangeburg, SC - 29115\n\nThey want to verify their SESO against ours. Inbra will be sending us their SESO so we can verify making emulsions with their SESO. They will also send us lecithin from  Brazil so we can verify that the SESO produced in Brazil can be emulsified with their Brazil sourced lecithin.",
